# ── LAN MySQL (XAMPP on server PC) ────────────────────────────────────────────
# Set DB_HOST_LAN to the IP of the PC running XAMPP on your local network.
# Find it with: ipconfig (Windows) → look for IPv4 under your Wi-Fi adapter
# Leave DB_PASSWORD_LAN blank if XAMPP root has no password (default).
